HEADWORD: dillenia
<hw>dillenia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of several evergreen trees or
shrubs of the genus <gen>Dillenia</gen> grown for their foliage and
nodding magnolialike flowers which are followed by fruit that is used in
curries and jellies and preserves.</def>⟦br⟧
